# A minimal and quick setup for using python on atom on macOS

In stylesheet,change the color of the comments

atom-text-editor .syntax--comment {
  color: cadetblue;
}


Theme: Atom Dark UI
Font: One Dark 

Packages for Python:

script - Run python on atom
Hydrogen - Make atom behave like Jupyter notebook
atom-python-virtualenv - Virtual env support
autocomplete - Suggestions while coding (Not the best in my opinion)
file-icons - Change the file icons

